name: Execute Playbook using Mock Data
description:
This reference block showcases an example of configuring a playbook where you add sample data and execute a playbook step simulating the sample data as output.

Note: To enable Mock Output, set variable value `useMockOutput` to `true`

Example: You might want the playbook that simulates output of malicious IP Addresses from VirusTotal.

arguments.name: VirusTotal
